---
layout: layouts/page.njk
---

<h1>Wish List</h1>

<p>I've been working on dropping Amazon from my life for a while now. While I haven't fully succeeded, I am keeping my Wish List off of their platform.</p>

<p>You're more than welcome to purchase the products on Amazon or through the retailers listed.</p>

<div class="wish-list">
  {% for item in wishlist.items | sort(attribute='priority') | reverse %}
    <div class="wish-item">
      <div class="wish-item__header">
        {% if item.link %}
          <h3 class="wish-item__title">
            <a href="{{ item.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.name }}</a>
          </h3>
        {% else %}
          <h3 class="wish-item__title">{{ item.name }}</h3>
        {% endif %}
        {% if item.priority %}
          <span class="wish-item__priority priority-{{ item.priority }}">Priority {{ item.priority }}</span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      
      {% if item.notes %}
        <div class="wish-item__description">
          {{ item.notes }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      
      <div class="wish-item__footer">
        {% if item.price %}
          <span class="wish-item__price">{{ item.price }}</span>
        {% endif %}
        {% if item.quantity %}
          <span class="wish-item__quantity">Qty: {{ item.quantity }}</span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
